        <scopecontent id="aspace_b2421a01ef6f67cf9502c185b66514d1">
          <head>Scope and Contents</head>
          <p>This volume contains the earliest administrative and membership records of the church.
            Included in the volume is the original covenant, meeting minutes, baptismal records, and
            disciplinary. Of particular note are records relating to accusations of premarital
            sexual relations. Also included are records related to the acceptance and dismission of
            deacons.</p>
        </scopecontent>
